<br />\n啲老野成日以為自己葉問一個打十個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個打十個飛機都無佢地份啦<br />\n三句唔埋兩句就講手，又唔係好打喎</blockquote><br />\n老野打架係零舍狼死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n狼死唔一定會贏既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盲拳都打死老師父啦<br />\n佢地幾廿歲人卜卜脆，捱得幾多下啊？"},{"pid":"0ed2d1c85200c9e11e61a9865fe6023f3098ad71","tid":122270,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:06:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9517cd5d7d425db1a8b7f542c8cbebd286adfd3a","tid":122270,"uid":60137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:07:39.000Z","msg":"以前同廢老嘈，撩到佢出手再報警驗傷好喇。錯手打死班豆腐廢老，搞到自己衰誤殺就無鳩謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ae47376602b8a64e51e2e1bf1d5a53bd02a845","tid":122270,"uid":60137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:08:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以<span style=\"color: red;\">後</span>同廢老嘈，撩到佢出手再報警驗傷好喇。錯手打死班豆腐廢老，搞到自己衰誤殺就無鳩謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a61221969e3d72f827fd451859e07f7e047fb2","tid":122270,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:08:31.000Z","msg":"咁都可以打一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地拎膠袋關你撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d4cda390ccf77330eec2c2ad8b9318edf8b303c","tid":122270,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:09:59.000Z","msg":"以為自己好打得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f317cad852c218d4d4d19e17e6ad3dafa45004e4","tid":122270,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislik