 />\n浪費膠袋係錯,都唔駛打死人架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個63歲既點估到後生過自己兩年既會咁豆腐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲老野成日以為自己葉問一個打十個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個打十個飛機都無佢地份啦<br />\n三句唔埋兩句就講手，又唔係好打喎</blockquote><br />\n老野打架係零舍狼死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n狼死唔一定會贏既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盲拳都打死老師父啦<br />\n佢地幾廿歲人卜卜脆，捱得幾多下啊？</blockquote><br />\n其實先60幾姐又唔算好老<br />\n成日同d老人家打波<br />\n屌你骨架硬到</blockquote><br />\n7、80都走水貨啦依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b052d753a7b20294d5b1f9eb80407c65cc90f069","tid":122270,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:12:57.000Z","msg":"點解d廢老咁鍾意玩出命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3959dae01ec24f43d4d0cfb2a547e462185eed11","tid":122270,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:19:07.000Z","msg":"在長洲北社街居住的61歲姓梁死者，生前有多種病患<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成家人安樂曬啦,唔洗照顧"},{"pid":"d5ff941550ea143b02ce30fa9a9925d2855b0529","tid":122270,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:24:16.000Z","msg":"廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09077c00c4dd4dcabae3c08bf6c60138ea43d20","tid":122270,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:29:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>在長洲北社街居住的61歲姓梁死者，生前有多種病患<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成家人安樂曬啦,唔洗照顧</blockquote><br />\n似係嬲得制激撚死左多過比人打死"},{"pid":"292fb314923f65dcf9df967326ba0afffa914e83","tid":